Reasoning: The paper proposes a novel domain adaptation method that utilizes attribute information to adapt to a target domain without target data. This involves reweighting the source data based on the attribute prior. The paper also provides theoretical analysis and experimental results. This work is relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and multimedia (cs.MM).
